<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA122294-0019 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 110249 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
December 22, 1994, Thursday, Southland Edition 
</P>
