<HEADLINE>
<P>
USC'S BOSEMAN ELIGIBLE AGAIN 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By LONNIE WHITE 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 USC sophomore Stais Boseman will play in next week's Seton Hall basketball 
tournament after regaining his eligibility, campus sources said. 
</P>
<P>
 Boseman was academically ineligible for the first six weeks of the season for 
the Trojans (4-4). 
</P>
<P>
 Boseman, a 6-foot-4 guard, led the team in steals as a freshman last season. 
LONNIE WHITE 
</P>
</TEXT>
