<P>
 FTC OKs Levi's Opening of Retail Stores: The clothing company won approval to 
open dozens of its own outlets. The ruling by the Federal Trade Commission also 
clears the way for a joint venture between the venerable San Francisco apparel 
maker and Designs Inc. Levi Strauss & Co. and Designs have been in talks aimed 
