 "I don't think anybody gives a darn, frankly."  
</P>
<P>
 -- Manhattan Beach City Councilman Jack Cunningham, on residents' response 
after the council voted to push back the municipal elections scheduled for 
April, 1996, giving some council members an extra 11 months in office. J3 
